  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售库存管理的流程图，核心是从库存开始，经过收银系统，再返回库存检查。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先放一个库存节点作为起点。接下来直接连到收银系统吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，从库存到收银系统，然后收银完成要再回到库存做一次扣减。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经连好了：库存→收银→再回到库存。现在需要做一个判断节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。回到库存后要判断库存是否充足，这里用一个菱形判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "菱形判断节点已添加，标注为库存检查。如果库存充足走哪条分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "充足的话继续往下走，进入订单管理系统。注意这里要有一个中间库存状态节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "中间库存状态节点是指判断后的那个库存节点吗？然后连到订单管理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，判断为\"是\"的分支先到库存状态节点，再到订单管理。订单管理后面还要再处理一次。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接：判断为是→库存状态→订单管理。订单管理后面是另一个订单管理节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，订单管理分两步，第一步处理订单，第二步处理完成后再回到库存做最终扣减。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两个订单管理节点已连好，第二个订单管理指向库存。接下来是优惠券系统的判断吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，最终扣减库存后要判断是否需要使用优惠券系统。这里再加一个菱形判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "优惠券系统的判断节点已添加。如果判断为\"是\"，流程怎么走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "使用优惠券的话，先进优惠券系统处理，然后还要再经过一次优惠券系统确认，最后回到收银系统完成交易。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "两个优惠券系统节点串联，然后指向收银系统。那如果判断为\"否\"呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不用优惠券的话，直接结束流程，回到一个终止库存节点。这个节点要和之前库存不足的情况共用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，库存不足的判断为\"否\"，和不使用优惠券的\"否\"分支，都指向同一个终止库存节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个逻辑。现在让我看看整体结构，确认一下第一个判断节点的\"否\"分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "第一个库存判断的\"否\"分支已连到终止库存节点。整体流程看起来完整了，我检查一下连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现一个问题。第一个判断节点之后的库存节点，和起始的库存节点，标签是不是重复了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确实，我检查一下...起始节点是库存，判断后的中间节点也是库存，终止节点还是库存。虽然标签相同，但在流程图中它们代表不同状态，需要保留。不过让我确认连接是否正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "连接应该没问题。但我注意到收银系统到库存的箭头，和后面回到收银系统的箭头，方向要搞清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我发现了，收银系统B到库存C的箭头我画对了，但让我再确认一下最后优惠券流程回到收银系统的连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "最后是从第二个优惠券系统节点K回到收银系统L，完成整个闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 26,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已确认，K到L的连接正确。现在所有分支都完整了：库存检查的两个分支，优惠券判断的两个分支，都汇聚到终止节点X。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 27,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，再确认一下判断节点的标签，\"Sí\"和\"No\"是西班牙语的是和否，这个没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 28,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，两个判断节点D和I的分支标签都是\"Sí\"和\"No\"。流程图已完成，从库存起点到收银终点，涵盖了库存检查、订单管理和优惠券系统三个核心模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 29,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个流程图准确反映了我们零售系统的业务逻辑，可以定稿了。",
